# Deutsche Post Email Forwarder

## Description

The Deutsche Post Email Forwarder is a program designed to automate the forwarding process of Deutsche Post emails regarding "Briefankündigung" to specified email addresses. It is tailored for users with GMX email accounts.

## How it Works

The program securely logs into the user's GMX email account using provided credentials. It then scans the inbox for emails from Deutsche Post with the subject line related to "Briefankündigung". Upon finding an eligible email, the program extracts its content and forwards it to the desired email addresses specified by the user.

## Prerequisites

- A GMX email account. If you don't have one, you can create it at [GMX](https://www.gmx.com/).

## Installation

1. Clone this repository to your local machine using `git clone`.
2. Export the source into a runnable JAR file and execute it.

## Important Notes

- This program is specifically designed for GMX email accounts and may not be compatible with other email providers.
- Keep your GMX email account credentials secure to protect your privacy and prevent unauthorized access.
- Ensure a stable internet connection while running the program for seamless operation.

